---
/**
 * Slim status strip rendered at the top of a draft post. The matching
 * pill on listing cards is .wu-pill-draft; both share the amber palette
 * defined in global.css.
 */
---
<aside class="draft-banner" role="note" aria-label="Draft notice">
  <span class="draft-banner-pill">Draft</span>
  <span class="draft-banner-text">Work in progress &middot; subject to change &middot; not indexed by search engines.</span>
</aside>
